{"tid":1560493,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：香港之歌，英治時代的文化傳承。","createTime":"2019-09-11T08:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T11:00:20.000Z","uid":69753,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46205d5870be408b5a30abf0b4d5e2cc0673ad56","tid":1560493,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">陳雲</span></ins>：香港之歌，英治時代的文化傳承。當時是戰後六十年代，楊慕琦總督發起的民主自治雖然失敗，但留下民選市政局及歌頌民主與自治的歌。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">對比起今日的所謂香港國歌，可見音樂與美學之沉淪</span>。當時《香港之歌》是商業電台製作而已，並不是香港政府或音樂學院，尋常的電台就可以製作到這種高水平的歌。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">文化是極高的修養與專業，不可以隨便冒犯。世上也只有香港人，隨便冒犯文化，只是共匪的痞子作風</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Qf-hFthH65A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQf-hFthH65A&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=b75f67ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Qf-hFthH65A</a>"},{"pid":"dbc93fef8bbb8f6a075a1888d13848fc37c1e662","tid":1560493,"uid":201464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T11:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/24/152112_1520d0fcbdd664fd69334cedb9a7a064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F24%2F152112_1520d0fcbdd664fd69334cedb9a7a064.jpg&h=d30124ed&s={SIZE}\" />同埋麻煩以後要睇陳雲偉論請去高登會員香江19度睇，直程係陳雲代言人<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/user/403064/posthistory\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fuser%2F403064%2Fposthistory&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=b29c74df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/user/403064/posthistory</a>"}]}